creator: i-aurora
descriptionHtml:
▷ 내가 원하는 사진과 문구로 나마네카드 제작!
▷ 대중교통 뿐만 아니라 오프라인 어디서나 결제!
▷ 잔액 충전/ 실시간 사용내역조회/ 카드 관리를 한 번에!

#취향듬뿍!! 넣은 카드만들기
: 원하는 디자인으로 세상에 단 하나뿐인 카드를 만들 수 있어요.

#빵빵~하게 카드충전하기
: 앱을 통해 직접 충전하거나 다른 분에게 충전을 요청해보세요.

#발 닿는 곳마다! 카드 사용하기
: 충전 후 대중교통과 오프라인 어디에서나 사용하실 수 있어요.

#못찾겠다 꾀꼬리~ 카드 관리하기
: 카드 일시잠금/ 분실신고 기능으로 걱정 없이 카드를 관리해보세요.

title: NAMANE 나마네카드

creator: i-aurora
descriptionHtml:
[NAMANE, All the travel in Korea]
▶ Create your own NAMANE CARD with your desired photo and text!
▶ Use NAMANE CARD for payment and public transportation anywhere in Korea!
▶ Top up balance, check transaction history, and manage card all in one app!

#Card Design
- Unleash your creativity on NAMANE CARD with the design of your choice.

#Pay Card Top-up
- Top up your payment balance anytime, anywhere through the app.
- Available Payment methods for Top-up: Int. Debit/Credit Card(VISA / MASTER / JCB), Int. Digital Payment(Alipay / Alipay+), Convenience Store(Cash), Coupon.

#NAMANE CARD Usage
- Pay Balance: Use NAMANE CARD anywhere in Korea!
> From convenience stores tocafes/restaurants, you can pay anywhere.
- Transit Balance: Travel with NAMANE CARD as a transportationcard!
> Use NAMANE CARD as a transportationcard, which is a must-have item whentraveling Korea.

#Pay Card History
- Check pay card balance and transaction history.

#Pay Card Transfer
- Transfer pay balance to another Korea account.
- Send pay balance by scanning the NAMAME QR code.

#Pay Card Move
- Move pay balance to another NAMANE CARD registered in your account.

#Kiosk Locations
- Locate the Kiosks where you can purchase and top-up NAMANE CARD on the map.

#Lock Card
- In case of loss, you can pause card on the app.
- When the card is set to paused status, it will prevent anyone else from using your balance.
- If you find the card, you can unpause the card to start using it again.
descriptionShort: [NAMANE, All the travel in Korea]

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Anyone can send money even if they are not Korean.
Conveniently send money while traveling in Korea.
No need to worry about complex bank names and account numbers in Korea.
You can easily and simply send money through QR scanning.

title:
NAMANE: Pay & Transit Card
3.3.8

creator: i-aurora
descriptionHtml:
[NAMANE, All the travel in Korea]
▶ Create your own NAMANE CARD with your desired photo and text!
▶ Use NAMANE CARD for payment and public transportation anywhere in Korea!
▶ Top up balance, check transaction history, and manage card all in one app!

#Card Design
- Unleash your creativity on NAMANE CARD with the design of your choice.

#Pay Card Top-up
- Top up your payment balance anytime, anywhere through the app.
- Available Payment methods for Top-up: Int. Debit/Credit Card(VISA / MASTER / JCB), Int. Digital Payment(Alipay / Alipay+), Convenience Store(Cash), Coupon.

#NAMANE CARD Usage
- Pay Balance: Use NAMANE CARD anywhere in Korea!
> From convenience stores tocafes/restaurants, you can pay anywhere.
- Transit Balance: Travel with NAMANE CARD as a transportationcard!
> Use NAMANE CARD as a transportationcard, which is a must-have item whentraveling Korea.

#Pay Card History
- Check pay card balance and transaction history.

#Pay Card Transfer
- Transfer pay balance to another Korea account.
- Send pay balance by scanning the NAMAME QR code.

#Pay Card Move
- Move pay balance to another NAMANE CARD registered in your account.

#Kiosk Locations
- Locate the Kiosks where you can purchase and top-up NAMANE CARD on the map.

#Lock Card
- In case of loss, you can pause card on the app.
- When the card is set to paused status, it will prevent anyone else from using your balance.
- If you find the card, you can unpause the card to start using it again.
